    "Heterogeneous graph networks can be used to integrate knowledge from different medical domains, including diseases and drugs, and incorporate their complex interactions (20), and machine learning (ML) methods, including graph neural networks, are now being applied to multimorbidity disease networks to improve disease diagnosis, treatment recommendation, and patient prognosis (21, 22)."
